summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical overhead and underground distribution easement over portions of Sunnydale Gardens, Division 1; Thormod's Addition; Hugo Smith's 5 Acre Tract; southwest quarter of Section 21, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; southwest quarter of Sec 4, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; and Tract 8, Crowell's Addition to the City of Seattle.
